            "answer_text": "Are you attractive? Talented in dancing and singing/rapping? Are you Korean? Is there something very unique about you? Are you younger than 18? If all of these apply to you then it is very very likely that most companies will accept you. But this can also just have to do with your timing. How good is the company financially? When did the company debut its last girl or boy group and when are they debuting there next? These are all factors to take in but if the all of the things first stated apple to you or at least all but one and the company is debuting a group in around a year then possibly. There is no telling for sure but of course there have been idols who have been accepted by multiple companies or trained at multiple. -A hungry potato ",
